## Tech stack (this project)

- Application code under `src` (e.g., `src/app`, `src/components`). Conventions: **botforge-fe-project-structure** (`components/` colocation, PascalCase component files).
- Tailwind CSS 4 + component primitives compatible with Shadcn/Radix patterns.
- Integrate new UI with existing tokens, layout, and `src/components/ui` patterns rather than one-off inline styles.
